Class Record

  • java.lang.Object
    • Record
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class Record
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents a record in the system. Each record contains a 'student-course' pair and the mark of the student.
